data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Situated on almost an acre of land, this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem offers a perfect blend of comfort and functionality. Inside, enjoy the cool ambiance with ceiling fans in the bedrooms and living room, complemented by tile plank flooring throughout. The kitchen is a culinary haven with ample storage. The property features a secure chain-link fence, providing privacy, and an outbuilding for added versatility. This home is more than just a residence; it's a lifestyle. Seize the opportunity to create a haven where memories are made and cherished. Welcome home! ???
